SEARCH
Package ProgettoLaboratorioB.Server

Interface ServerInterface

All Superinterfaces:
Remote
All Known Implementing Classes:
ServerImpl
public interface ServerInterface extends Remote
Server interface define the methods that the server must implement, in order to be used by the client from another virtual machine, by extending remote interface.
